text: Olga Vargas (born 18 March 1980) is a Mexican former synchronized swimmer. Olga competed in the women's duet at the 2004 Olympic Games with her partner Nara Falcón and finished in sixteenth place. == References == Category:1980 births Category:Living people Category:Mexican synchronized swimmers Category:Olympic synchronized swimmers of Mexico Category:Synchronized swimmers at the 2004 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Mexico City Category:Synchronized swimmers at the 2003 Pan American Games
